1616
01:36:52,423 --> 01:36:53,378
(barking)

1617
01:37:00,383 --> 01:37:01,338
Get down!

1618
01:37:01,423 --> 01:37:02,617
Aagh!

1619
01:37:18,183 --> 01:37:20,014
(screaming)

1620
01:37:21,383 --> 01:37:23,294
Six knots!

1621
01:37:33,863 --> 01:37:36,980
Aagh!

1622
01:37:41,263 --> 01:37:42,093
Aagh!

1623
01:37:42,183 --> 01:37:43,980
Oooh!

1624
01:37:45,703 --> 01:37:48,581
What? What? I can't hear you.

1625
01:37:51,983 --> 01:37:53,098
Aagh!

1626
01:37:56,983 --> 01:37:59,053
It's coming.

1627
01:38:07,583 --> 01:38:09,301
Five knots!

1628
01:38:15,263 --> 01:38:16,776
(barking)

1629
01:38:22,183 --> 01:38:23,411
(both) Ooh!

1630
01:38:33,023 --> 01:38:34,376
(horn blares)

1631
01:38:36,263 --> 01:38:38,697
(horn blares)

1632
01:38:40,863 --> 01:38:42,137
Four...

1633
01:38:42,223 --> 01:38:43,451
...aagh!

1634
01:38:44,583 --> 01:38:45,493
Stop!

1635
01:38:53,263 --> 01:38:55,254
Here it comes now!

1636
01:38:58,023 --> 01:38:58,899
It's really big, Mum.

1637
01:38:58,983 --> 01:39:00,496
Oh, my God!

1638
01:39:01,863 --> 01:39:03,091
Oh, my God!

1639
01:39:07,263 --> 01:39:08,298
Get down!

1640
01:39:09,983 --> 01:39:11,780
Aagh!

1641
01:39:33,263 --> 01:39:35,174
Aagh!

1642
01:39:37,583 --> 01:39:39,141
Two knots!

1643
01:39:39,223 --> 01:39:40,656
Almost stopped!

1644
01:39:53,103 --> 01:39:54,058
(barking)

1645
01:39:57,703 --> 01:39:58,852
Oh, no!

1646
01:40:03,823 --> 01:40:05,461
Get down!

1647
01:40:08,263 --> 01:40:10,174
(rings)

1648
01:40:16,223 --> 01:40:17,178
Zero.

1649
01:40:51,983 --> 01:40:53,462
Aagh! Aagh! Ooh.

1650
01:40:56,623 --> 01:40:59,183
(car alarm)

1651
01:40:59,263 --> 01:41:01,299
My car!

1652
01:41:05,383 --> 01:41:06,941
(barks)

1653
01:41:07,023 --> 01:41:08,979
I got to find Annie.

1654
01:41:20,423 --> 01:41:22,175
(Juliano) Shit! She's going over!

1655
01:41:22,263 --> 01:41:24,299
(screaming)

1656
01:41:24,383 --> 01:41:25,896
(Dante) We're tipping!

1657
01:41:25,983 --> 01:41:26,893
We're tipping!

1658
01:41:26,983 --> 01:41:28,462
(screaming)

1659
01:41:40,663 --> 01:41:42,176
Ow.

1660
01:41:46,863 --> 01:41:48,421
We're docked.

1661
01:41:49,583 --> 01:41:51,221
We're docked!

1662
01:41:51,303 --> 01:41:52,622
I can't believe it!

1663
01:41:52,703 --> 01:41:54,182
We're safe.

1664
01:42:06,983 --> 01:42:07,972
Zero.

1665
01:42:09,583 --> 01:42:11,460
(creaking)

1666
01:42:15,063 --> 01:42:17,054
(shouts)

1667
01:42:17,143 --> 01:42:18,462
Say what?

1668
01:42:18,543 --> 01:42:20,613
Bad luck to run ship over town.

1669
01:42:20,703 --> 01:42:22,295
No shit, bad luck, man.

1670
01:42:22,383 --> 01:42:24,897
I just bought a condo here.

1671
01:42:24,983 --> 01:42:27,099
My God.

1672
01:42:27,183 --> 01:42:29,014
You all right?

1673
01:42:29,103 --> 01:42:32,015
Yeah. I think I broke my other arm.

1674
01:42:32,103 --> 01:42:34,492
The ship's parked in the middle of town...

1675
01:42:34,583 --> 01:42:36,733
...but, hey, it could've been worse.

1676
01:42:36,823 --> 01:42:39,576
I'm not sure how,
but it could've been worse.

1677
01:42:39,663 --> 01:42:41,301
I got to get my girl.

1678
01:42:41,383 --> 01:42:42,293
Thank you.

1679
01:42:44,023 --> 01:42:45,092
Uh!

1680
01:42:45,183 --> 01:42:46,218
Sorry.

1681
01:42:47,183 --> 01:42:48,616
Be careful.

1682
01:42:49,583 --> 01:42:51,301
I'll go check on the others.

1683
01:43:03,623 --> 01:43:06,091
Looks like your vacation is almost over.

1684
01:43:06,183 --> 01:43:08,492
Just stay away from me,
or you're going to get hurt...

1685
01:43:08,583 --> 01:43:09,572
...I swear to God.

1686
01:43:09,663 --> 01:43:11,176
What are you going to do, Annie?

1687
01:43:11,263 --> 01:43:13,333
Splash water on me?

1688
01:43:22,783 --> 01:43:23,693
I'm driving now.

1689
01:43:23,783 --> 01:43:25,774
Hey, Annie! Hey!

1690
01:43:26,903 --> 01:43:28,495
Annie!

1691
01:43:28,583 --> 01:43:30,619
Come back! You stay with me!

1692
01:43:30,703 --> 01:43:32,295
You're my hostage!

1693
01:43:32,383 --> 01:43:34,180
I need a boat!

1694
01:43:37,103 --> 01:43:38,502
Can I help you?

1695
01:43:38,583 --> 01:43:40,938
I'm a cop. I need to borrow your boat.

1696
01:43:41,023 --> 01:43:43,139
What? You've got to be kidding me.

1697
01:43:43,223 --> 01:43:45,976
This is joke, right?
You're messing with my head.

1698
01:43:46,063 --> 01:43:47,860
Come on, man, you gotta be kidding me!

1699
01:43:48,983 --> 01:43:50,098
Can't you see I'm on a date?

1700
01:43:50,183 --> 01:43:53,573
Alex Shaw, LAPD. Start the boat.

1701
01:43:53,663 --> 01:43:54,937
LAPD? I'm in the Caribbean, man.

1702
01:43:55,023 --> 01:43:56,012
What are you doing here?

1703
01:43:57,063 --> 01:43:58,576
Stop him, Maurice.

1704
01:43:58,663 --> 01:44:00,938
Know how many hours of therapy
I've had because of you guys?

1705
01:44:01,023 --> 01:44:01,899
And that shit's expensive!

1706
01:44:01,983 --> 01:44:02,813
You drive.

1707
01:44:02,903 --> 01:44:04,302
(woman) Hey, hey, where are you going?

1708
01:44:04,383 --> 01:44:06,453
No!

1709
01:44:18,623 --> 01:44:20,181
Hey! Annie!

1710
01:44:30,263 --> 01:44:32,174
OK, OK, take it easy, man!

1711
01:44:32,263 --> 01:44:35,175
This boat cost me $150,000.

1712
01:44:38,903 --> 01:44:40,894
That way.

1713
01:44:40,983 --> 01:44:43,178
(Maurice) OK. That's it!

1714
01:44:43,263 --> 01:44:46,141
I want a promissory note right now!

1715
01:44:46,223 --> 01:44:47,781
(woman) Whoa!

1716
01:45:02,903 --> 01:45:03,779
Give it!

1717
01:45:03,863 --> 01:45:05,899
Let go of me!

1718
01:45:05,983 --> 01:45:06,813
Ow!

1719
01:45:06,903 --> 01:45:08,700
Do we have a fiery temper?

1720
01:45:08,783 --> 01:45:10,182
You have no idea!

1721
01:45:10,263 --> 01:45:12,174
(Geiger) There she is.

1722
01:45:12,263 --> 01:45:14,060
Look! Fireworks!

1723
01:45:16,263 --> 01:45:17,173
It's her.

1724
01:45:17,263 --> 01:45:18,139
What?

1725
01:45:18,223 --> 01:45:19,099
That way, fast.

1726
01:45:19,183 --> 01:45:20,298
Nah, I can't drive that fast!

1727
01:45:20,383 --> 01:45:21,896
There's shallow reefs! Shit!

1728
01:45:25,423 --> 01:45:27,379
(starts engine)

1729
01:45:41,903 --> 01:45:43,814
Get as close to that plane as you can.

1730
01:45:43,903 --> 01:45:46,019
Give me one good reason.

1731
01:45:46,103 --> 01:45:48,378
If you don't, I'll throw you over.

1732
01:45:48,463 --> 01:45:49,498
OK.

1733
01:45:49,583 --> 01:45:50,982
That's a good reason.

1734
01:46:01,023 --> 01:46:02,934
Almost at speed!

1735
01:46:03,023 --> 01:46:04,342
Don't! Don't you...

1736
01:46:04,423 --> 01:46:06,334
Ow! Let me go!

1737
01:46:06,423 --> 01:46:09,301
I think you better stay with me.

1738
01:46:09,383 --> 01:46:10,532
Get closer!

1739
01:46:10,623 --> 01:46:11,976
What?

1740
01:46:23,263 --> 01:46:24,378
Let me go!

1741
01:46:24,463 --> 01:46:26,181
You want to go? I'll let you go...

1742
01:46:26,263 --> 01:46:28,493
...at about 10,000 feet!

1743
01:46:28,583 --> 01:46:30,380
Get me closer!

1744
01:46:32,783 --> 01:46:33,772
Huh?

1745
01:46:33,863 --> 01:46:35,057
He's going to shoot the plane!

1746
01:46:37,903 --> 01:46:39,541
Nice shot.

1747
01:46:41,983 --> 01:46:45,532
Let's see if he can hold on now!

1748
01:46:45,623 --> 01:46:47,295
Follow me!

1749
01:46:56,503 --> 01:46:58,095
Let go!

1750
01:46:58,183 --> 01:46:59,502
He... he's supposed to let go.

1751
01:46:59,583 --> 01:47:00,777
Let go!

1752
01:47:02,583 --> 01:47:05,177
No, no, he's reeling himself in!

1753
01:47:05,263 --> 01:47:07,697
Follow him! Follow him!

1754
01:47:09,023 --> 01:47:11,696
Oh, you little shit.

1755
01:47:11,783 --> 01:47:13,774
Here we go!

1756
01:47:15,503 --> 01:47:16,902
(Geiger) No!

1757
01:47:16,983 --> 01:47:18,575
No, don't!

1758
01:47:18,663 --> 01:47:19,652
No!

1759
01:47:21,023 --> 01:47:22,979
Come here!

1760
01:47:23,063 --> 01:47:25,293
Oh, God.

1761
01:47:43,703 --> 01:47:45,819
Alex! Alex!

1762
01:47:45,903 --> 01:47:48,258
Annie!

1763
01:47:48,743 --> 01:47:50,256
Annie!

1764
01:48:02,223 --> 01:48:04,657
- Hi.
- (Annie) Hi.

1765
01:48:04,743 --> 01:48:05,812
Hi.

1766
01:48:06,463 --> 01:48:08,738
Come on.

1767
01:48:15,863 --> 01:48:16,978
Now hold on!

1768
01:48:18,783 --> 01:48:20,057
Aagh!

1769
01:48:23,703 --> 01:48:25,341
What's he riding that banana peel for?

1770
01:48:25,423 --> 01:48:26,492
What's he doing?

1771
01:48:29,263 --> 01:48:31,493
Aagh!

1772
01:48:50,503 --> 01:48:51,458
Aagh!

1773
01:48:54,263 --> 01:48:56,982
Aagh!

1774
01:48:59,183 --> 01:49:00,582
(siren)

1775
01:49:00,663 --> 01:49:01,937
(PA) Abandon ship.

1776
01:49:02,023 --> 01:49:03,615
All the crew members...

1777
01:49:03,703 --> 01:49:05,580
...abandon ship immediately.

1778
01:49:05,663 --> 01:49:07,733
(Maurice) It's gonna blow, it's gonna blow!

1779
01:49:07,823 --> 01:49:09,575
Jump, fool! Get off that thing!

1780
01:49:10,583 --> 01:49:11,459
Jump!

1781
01:49:40,663 --> 01:49:42,938
Hope they can hold their breath
a long time.

1782
01:49:43,023 --> 01:49:45,491
Come on, don't run out of air.

1783
01:49:45,583 --> 01:49:48,017
Me not see 'em. Me think they dead.

1784
01:49:48,103 --> 01:49:49,582
They're not gone.

1785
01:50:09,663 --> 01:50:12,700
(woman) There they are! There they are!

1786
01:50:12,783 --> 01:50:13,693
(Maurice) Hey, over here!

1787
01:50:13,783 --> 01:50:14,977
Hey, this way!

1788
01:50:30,263 --> 01:50:32,572
Here, come on. I got you. Come on.

1789
01:50:32,663 --> 01:50:33,698
Come on, hurry up.

1790
01:50:33,783 --> 01:50:35,102
Hurry up, come on. It's gonna blow.

1791
01:50:35,183 --> 01:50:36,980
Hurry up, it's gonna blow.

1792
01:50:41,103 --> 01:50:42,582
Aagh!

1793
01:51:02,063 --> 01:51:04,099
Untie 'em, untie 'em.

1794
01:51:04,183 --> 01:51:05,502
You're all right.

1795
01:51:07,383 --> 01:51:09,374
- You OK?
- Yeah.

1796
01:51:09,463 --> 01:51:11,772
I was just so scared. I was so scared.

1797
01:51:11,863 --> 01:51:15,219
I didn't think
I was gonna make it there for a second.

1798
01:51:18,783 --> 01:51:19,977
Thank you.

1799
01:51:24,503 --> 01:51:29,213
Look what I found in international waters.

1800
01:51:29,303 --> 01:51:31,373
This really is paradise.

1801
01:51:31,463 --> 01:51:33,499
I got something for you.

1802
01:51:39,183 --> 01:51:40,980
Oh.

1803
01:51:42,583 --> 01:51:43,413
Wow.

1804
01:51:43,503 --> 01:51:46,415
You want to wear this for a while?

1805
01:51:49,183 --> 01:51:52,300
How long were you thinking?

1806
01:51:52,383 --> 01:51:53,816
50 years.

1807
01:51:53,903 --> 01:51:54,858
Yeah?

1808
01:51:56,183 --> 01:51:57,377
Yeah.

1809
01:52:06,663 --> 01:52:09,416
Can I make all the travel plans
from now on?

1810
01:52:09,503 --> 01:52:10,697
Deal.

1811
01:52:43,863 --> 01:52:45,057
# Jimmy Cliff:
You Can Get It If You Really Want

1812
01:52:45,143 --> 01:52:47,737
# You can get it, if you really want

1813
01:52:48,183 --> 01:52:52,381
# You can get it, if you really want

1814
01:52:52,463 --> 01:52:55,182
# You can get it, if you really want

1815
01:52:55,263 --> 01:52:56,298
# But you must try...

1816
01:52:56,383 --> 01:52:57,338
Hello.

1817
01:52:57,423 --> 01:52:59,493
Mr Kenter.

1818
01:52:59,583 --> 01:53:00,538
Oh, Annie.

1819
01:53:00,623 --> 01:53:03,774
- Uh... Oh, you're back again.
- Yeah.

1820
01:53:03,863 --> 01:53:05,012
Hope you don't mind.

1821
01:53:05,103 --> 01:53:06,536
I kind of requested you.

1822
01:53:06,623 --> 01:53:09,740
I wanted to make up for last week.

1823
01:53:09,823 --> 01:53:11,017
Why would I mind?

1824
01:53:11,103 --> 01:53:14,015
Gosh, uh...
I'm sure it'll go much better today.

1825
01:53:14,103 --> 01:53:15,218
Oh, yeah, it will.

1826
01:53:15,303 --> 01:53:17,692
- Had some problems.
- Nervous, yeah, a little bit.

1827
01:53:17,783 --> 01:53:19,694
OK, Mr Kenter, here we go.

1828
01:53:32,823 --> 01:53:35,542
Sorry, but that bus was going way too fast.

1829
01:53:35,623 --> 01:53:38,342
I noticed that. Uh, make a left here.

1830
01:53:38,423 --> 01:53:39,538
Got it. Excuse me.

1831
01:53:39,623 --> 01:53:43,218
Thank you, thank you.

1832
